Usage: FORMAT SEND_ACTION <format description>
  Controls how CTCP ACTIONs appear when sent.

  Valid format characters:
       F          Nick of person doing action (your nick)
       T          Nick of person receiving action
       M          The action message

See Also:  
  ME
  DESCRIBE
